## Naming Conventions

> Teknolojiye ozel naming convention'lar ilgili tech-pack `.mdc` dosyasinda tanimlanir.
> Asagidakiler tum teknolojiler icin gecerli **genel** kurallardir.

- **API Endpoints:** kebab-case plural (`/api/v1/order-items`)
- **API Query Params:** camelCase (`pageSize`, `sortBy`)
- **Environment Variables:** UPPER_SNAKE_CASE (`API_BASE_URL`, `DB_CONNECTION`)
- **Feature Flags:** PascalCase + Enabled suffix (`TwoFactorEnabled`)
- **DB Tables:** PascalCase plural (`Orders`, `OrderItems`)
- **DB Columns:** PascalCase (`CreatedAt`, `TenantId`)

---

## API Standartlari
- RESTful: GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, PATCH
- Versiyonlama: `/api/v1/...` (URL-based)
- Response: `Result<T>` wrapper (`IsSuccess`, `Message`, `Data`, `Errors`)
- Pagination: `PagedResult<T>` (`Items`, `TotalCount`, `Page`, `PageSize`)
- Sorting: `?sort=createdAt:desc` veya `?sort=status:asc,createdAt:desc`
- Filtering: `?filters[status]=active&filters[categoryId]=xxx`
- ProblemDetails (RFC 7807) for errors
- Headers: `X-Correlation-Id`, `X-Request-Duration-Ms`, `X-RateLimit-*`

### HTTP Status Codes
```
200 OK          -> GET, PUT, PATCH
201 Created     -> POST (Location header ile)
204 No Content  -> DELETE
400 Bad Request -> Validation hatasi
401 Unauthorized -> Token yok/gecersiz
403 Forbidden   -> Yetki yok
404 Not Found   -> Entity bulunamadi
409 Conflict    -> Duplicate / Concurrency
422 Unprocessable -> Is kurali ihlali
429 Too Many    -> Rate limit (Retry-After header)
500 Internal    -> Beklenmeyen hata (ASLA detay gosterme)
```

